title: Captain Fantastic
overview: In the forests of the Pacific Northwest, a father devoted to raising his six kids with a rigorous physical and intellectual education is forced to leave his paradise and enter the world, challenging his idea of what it means to be a parent.

title: Chhichhore
overview: A tragic incident forces Anirudh, a middle-aged man, to take a trip down memory lane and reminisce his college days along with his friends, who were labelled as losers.

title: Little Miss Sunshine
overview: A family determined to get their young daughter into the finals of a beauty pageant take a cross-country trip in their VW bus.

title: Manhattan
overview: The life of a divorced television writer dating a teenage girl is further complicated when he falls in love with his best friend's mistress.

title: Happiness
overview: The lives of several individuals intertwine as they go about their lives in their own unique ways, engaging in acts society as a whole might find disturbing in a desperate search for human connection.

title: Vizontele
overview: Lives of residents in a small Anatolian village change when television is introduced to them

title: Perfetti sconosciuti
overview: Seven long-time friends get together for a dinner. When they decide to share with each other the content of every text message, email and phone call they receive, many secrets start to unveil and the equilibrium trembles.

title: OMG: Oh My God!
overview: A shopkeeper takes God to court when his shop is destroyed by an earthquake.

title: Jojo Rabbit
overview: A young boy in Hitler's army finds out his mother is hiding a Jewish girl in their home.

title: The Quiet Man
overview: A retired American boxer returns to the village of his birth in Ireland, where he falls for a spirited redhead whose brother is contemptuous of their union.

title: The Breakfast Club
overview: Five high school students meet in Saturday detention and discover how they have a lot more in common than they thought.

title: Harvey
overview: Due to his insistence that he has an invisible six foot-tall rabbit for a best friend, a whimsical middle-aged man is thought by his family to be insane - but he may be wiser than anyone knows.

title: Miracle on 34th Street
overview: When a nice old man who claims to be Santa Claus is institutionalized as insane, a young lawyer decides to defend him by arguing in court that he is the real thing.

title: Kal Ho Naa Ho
overview: Naina, an introverted, perpetually depressed girl's life changes when she meets Aman. But Aman has a secret of his own which changes their lives forever. Embroiled in all this is Rohit, Naina's best friend who conceals his love for her.
stars: ['Preity Zinta', 'Shah Rukh Khan', 'Saif Ali Khan', 'Jaya Bachchan']

title: The Truman Show
overview: An insurance salesman discovers his whole life is actually a reality TV show.

title: Yeopgijeogin geunyeo
overview: A young man sees a drunk, cute woman standing too close to the tracks at a metro station in Seoul and pulls her back. She ends up getting him into trouble repeatedly after that, starting on the train.

title: Silver Linings Playbook
overview: After a stint in a mental institution, former teacher Pat Solitano moves back in with his parents and tries to reconcile with his ex-wife. Things get more challenging when Pat meets Tiffany, a mysterious girl with problems of her own.

title: Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara
overview: Three friends decide to turn their fantasy vacation into reality after one of their friends gets engaged.

title: Sabrina
overview: A playboy becomes interested in the daughter of his family's chauffeur, but it's his more serious brother who would be the better man for her.

title: La règle du jeu
overview: A bourgeois life in France at the onset of World War II, as the rich and their poor servants meet up at a French chateau.
